text: Food Network Star Kids is an American cooking competition television series that aired on Food Network, presented by actress Tia Mowry and food critic Donal Skehan. The series is a spin-off of Food Network Star. ==Contestants== ===Winner=== * Amber Kelley - Seattle, Washington ===Runners-up=== * Isaiah Hooks - Stroudsburg, Pennsylvania * Liam Waldman - Los
